  "title": "Uruguayan Sloe Berries Lasagna",
  "description": "A dense and cozy Uruguayan dish featuring sloe berries, cheese, and pasta, all wrapped in a banana leaf. This satvik friendly recipe is perfect for a cold winter night.",
