  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees.",
    "Cook the lasagna noodles according to package instructions.",
    "In a bowl, mix together the ricotta cheese, mozzarella cheese, and parmesan cheese.",
    "Add the sloe berries to the cheese mixture and stir well.",
    "Brush the banana leaves with olive oil and place a sheet of lasagna noodle on each leaf.",
    "Spread a quarter of the cheese and sloe berry mixture on each noodle.",
    "Repeat the layers three more times, ending with a layer of cheese on top.",
    "Fold the banana leaves over the lasagna and secure with toothpicks.",
    "Bake for 30 minutes and serve hot."
  ],
